csum=You will be naked (including no skillbook) until you loot your corpse, but you may ask others to use skills for you like summon temporary items for you or give you food or drink.  Good samaritan players may hang out at bind points helping those that wake up dead. Perhaps a high level Water skill (that has ~20 required of each of the 4 relevant stats) can be "heavenly garb" which clones your original gear temporarily from your corpse.  A high level Air spell of the same caliber can be "angelic wings" which allows a recently dead character to float above the aggro zone of every monster for a limited time.  A high level Earth spell of the same caliber could be "total recall" where a recently dead group member player is instantly transported to the caster via gravity tunnel that opens in the earth, or total recall can instead be you gain a temporary clone of your skillbook for use on your journey.  A high level Fire spell of the same caliber could be "fumes of Ichor" where monsters cannot see you for a limited time unless you are standing right on top of them (but you have to be naked), and if they do swing at you they are more likely to miss. 
