ing the game in first person, but you can take a look at your character often if you want.  There will be no "over the shoulder" or isometric 3rd person orbirds eye view that would distract from the immersion of **bieng** your character.  Also I want monsters to be able to sneak up on the character and surprise them if they aren't constantly looking around.  And looking around doesn't mean "go into 100ft birds eye view to make sure there is nothing around you" it would mean actually turning around and looking around you.%0a
