diff:1657662078:1657661769:=80c80%0a%3c Roll 3d6 7 times and choose the top 4 3d6 rolls and assign to the 4 personality traits of your class however you decide.  Discard lowest 3 of the 3d6 rolls.  This is done so that someone buying multiple NFT's to reroll won't have a significant advantage as someone who only has one NFT.  Also this method allows you to pick your class which old school D&D pretty much didn't let you do.%0a---%0a> Roll 3d6 7 times and choose the top 4 3d6 rolls and assign to the 4 personality traits of your class however you decide.  Discard lowest 3 of the 3d6 rolls.%0a
