diff:1657557180:1657557028:=68c68%0a%3c #Charmed monsters can be directed (moved) by the user (or others by Ni skill) but formulated monsters cannot be moved by their creator since they lack Ni.  Charmed monsters must be charmed in battle and only last as long as that battle (at most).  Formulated (summoned or constructed) monsters act of their own accord but can be inspired by the creator or others (using Ne skills) of what they should be doing. Formulated creatures can be directed (moved) by Ni users, but the formulator doesn't have Ni themself. Formulated monsters last for an extended period.  Ne skills can inspire summoned or charmed monsters to do things like defend, attack, guard, follow, and so on.%0a---%0a> #Difference between charmed monsters and formulated monsters is charmed can be directed (moved) by the user (or others by Ni skill) but formulated monsters cannot be moved by their creator.  Charmed monsters must be charmed in battle and only last as long as that battle (at most).  Formulated (summoned or constructed) monsters act of their own accord but can be inspired by the creator or others (using Ne skills) of what they should be doing. Formulated creatures can be directed (moved) by Ni users, but the formulator doesn't have Ni themself. Formulated monsters last for an extended period.  Ne skills can inspire summoned or charmed monsters to do things like defend, attack, guard, and so on.%0a
